data.strFullDescription:
CUCKOLD SIMULATOR, the exciting new game where you play as Cuckold (that is his name) in his day-to-day life.

[h2]Features[/h2]

[list][*] Work your job at GloboCorp to make money
[*] You can give all your hard-earned money to the bull
[*] Browse your favorite websites, such as Reddit™
[*] Your fat wife will verbally abuse you
[*] Become emotionally attached to children that are not biologically yours
[*] Collect 'Funky Pop' collectibles that are hidden across the world
[*] Play actual games on your 'Wintendo Snitch' gaming console, such as 'Cuck Souls'
[*] And more!
[/list]

[img]https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1141550/extras/family.png?t=1665851104[/img]

[h2]One Happy Family[/h2]

[list][*] [b]Cuckold[/b] - Husband and beta male provider of the family. Only good for providing income. 
[*] [b]Wife[/b] - Fat and mean. Only has eyes for Tyrone - and Cuckold's wallet.
[*] [b]Tyrone[/b] - Transient alpha male of the household. Has outstanding warrants.
[*] [b]DeShawn[/b] - Wife's ten year old child from a previous relationship. Does not respect Cuckold.
[*] [b]Tyrone Jr.[/b] - The newest addition to the family. Named after his father. Too young to not respect Cuckold.[/list]

[h2]Wintendo Snitch[/h2]

The Wintendo Snitch is a fully functional game console that you can purchase inside of the game. Play exciting games such as [b]CUCK SOULS[/b] or Anime Girl Genocide. Truly a treat for fans of the soulsborne genre. More games to be released eventually.

[img]https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1141550/extras/cucksouls.gif?t=1665851104[/img]
[img]https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1141550/extras/cuck-souls-transparent.png?t=1665851104[/img]
